defaultMessage: allows owners to choose among three standardized cancellation policies (Flexible, Moderate, and Strict) that Will be enforced to protect both renter and owner alike. Renters may cancel and review any penalties by viewing their travel plans and then clicking ‘Cancel’ on the appropriate reservation. A owner will be able to see the number of reservations a renter has Cancelled over the previous 12 months when the renter submits Booking request.

Locatários pode cancelar e rever quaisquer penalidades, visualizando seus planos de viagem e, em seguida, clicando em ‘Cancelar’ na reserva apropriado.
